Melanie Fullerton https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Melanie_Fullerton 0 Melanie Fullerton was an actress in the late 1960s and early 1970s. She starred in Night of the Lepus along with Stuart Whitman as well as co-starred in To Rome With Love with John Forsythe, Vito Scotti, Joyce Menges, and Susan Neher.
